    <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="innerpagetexttitle">Overview</span> </div>
        <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">We believe that financial planning stands for people, their dreams and their goals.<br /><br/>
Established in early 2009, Ffreedom Financial Planners is part of India’s modern breed of true unbiased client focused Financial Planning Firms. The team at Ffreedom has a vision to empower its clients through quality unbiased financial advice, latest technology that helps clients with their personal financial management &amp; also assisting them in realizing all their dreams and converting them into realistic achievable goals.</span></div>
<div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage"><strong>Facilitators for you</strong></span></div>
   <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
   We work in collaboration with our clients as facilitators in the cause to bring about financial freedom to them. At Ffreedom, we have developed unique models for our clients needs from a financial plan viewpoint. Our planners are dedicated in their effort to bridge the gap between your income generation and sustenance of wealth. Our advice does not only restrict to financial products or investments for goals, we advice our clients with regards to multiple aspects of their lives that have a direct or indirect impact on their financial health.<br /><br/> 
We define Financial Planning as much more than a computer generated algorithm. It is one of the few disciplines that can lay claim to being a science and art at the same time. We at Ffreedom create simple and realistic financial plans which are easy to execute.
   </span></div>
<div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage"><strong>Our Commitment:</strong></span> </div>      
   <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
   Providing measureable and executable strategies to our clients to ensure they progress towards realizing their goals. Our strength lies in providing clients with a comprehensive financial plan, consolidated reports for all financial investments and an end-to-end solution bringing convenience.
    </span></div>
    <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage"><strong>The first step of freedom</strong></span> </div>
   <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
   Ffreedom was founded by Sumeet Vaid along with a team of highly experienced team of professionals. The vision of this group was to create a firm that acts as an all-inclusive system that meets with all the requirements related to financial management that a client might have. With an insight that people needed a service that could be customized to provide them independence from financial hardships and in this manner provide a wholesome and stress free life void of financial worries to all the clients.
    </span></div> 
<div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage"><strong>The 3D approach to financial planning</strong></span></div> 
   <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
 With our unique proprietary model ‘Dream > Decide > Do’ we act as enablers for our clients bridging the gap between desiring and accomplishing.</span></div>
  <div class="innerpage_litext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">
   <li><strong>Dream:</strong> Everything begins with a dream. Our planners encourage you to dream more</li>
   <li><strong>Decide:</strong> List your dreams and then prioritize your goals </li>
     <li><strong>Do:</strong> Our planners assist you in formulating and executing your plan </li>
    </span></div>
    <div class="innerpage_titletext"><span class="txtmatterbig_innerpage">By using the Dream > Decide > Do model we help you plan today for a better tomorrow. Hence our aim is to equip you to <strong>“Live your dreams”</strong>.</span><br/><br />
